products.title: Clams Casino Stuffed Pasta Shells
products.description: Clams Casino Stuffed Pasta Shells are a twist on one of my childhood appetizer favorites - clams casino. Bacon, clams, peppers, cream, and cheese are stuffed into pasta shells for a truly incredible dinner.

products.title: Peri Peri Chicken
products.description: This peri peri chicken is made with my take on African peri peri sauce using fresh and dried chiles. The marinade is incredibly flavorful and gives the chicken a beautiful color as well.

products.title: Miso Beef Noodles
products.description: This extremely flavorful, savory noodle dish is inspired by any and all regions’ noodle dishes I’ve ever had along with dishes featuring miso.

products.title: Southeast Asian Style Chicken Rice
products.description: I've mixed elements of Vietnamese, Thai, Indonesian and other Asian cuisines to make a delicious chicken and rice dish topped with a fresh herb salad.

products.title: How to Make Pie: Nicole's Best Tips
products.description: Demystify the pie! Nicole McLaughlin, aka Nicole Mcmom, shares her best tips for making pies, from crusts and fillings to baking and serving.

products.title: Smart Tips and Winning Recipes for Successful Bake Sales
products.description: Bake sales are tried-and-false fundraisers that rely on the irresistible appeal of home-baked treats to bring in the bucks for your group or cause. Of course, they also rely on good planning and organization. To ensure your event is a sweet success, we have some no-fail bake sale ideas -- tips for pulling together a bake sale and, of course, crowd-pleasing recipe suggestions -- the bake sale best sellers!
